text: William Andrew van Wyk (born ) is a South African rugby union player that played first class rugby for the in 2016. He made six appearances in the 2016 Currie Cup qualification series, and a single appearance in the 2016 Currie Cup Premier Division. He also represented South Africa Schools in 2009.
